### Sample Input
```
1  # Show Devices
1  # Select first device (Smartphone)
2  # Enter quantity
2  # Show Cart
3  # Checkout
```

### Sample Output
```
iPhone 13 - $999 - Stock: 10 - Warranty: 24 months - Screen: 6.1" - Battery: 20h
Added 2 iPhone 13 to cart.
iPhone 13 - Quantity: 2
Total price: $1998
Purchase successful! Total price: $1998
```

